<% provide(:title, "About") %>

<div class="center">
  <h1>About Discover Hockey</h1>

  <h4>
    <%= link_to "Discover Hockey", root_path %> is a site designed for hockey card enthusiasts. 
    Optionally, site users can link to 
    <a href="http://stores.ebay.ca/Garrison-Hockey-Cards/Vancouver-Canucks-/_i.html?_fsub=20625816" target="_blank">Garrison Cards</a>
    on eBay to buy, sell or trade cards.
  </h4><br>

  <div class="center jumbotron">
    <%= image_tag "turris-coyotes.jpg" %>
  </div>

  <p>
    The site extends concepts learned from the <a href="http://www.railstutorial.org" target="_blank">Ruby on Rails Tutorial</a>, RailsGuide Blog and related resources.
  </p>
  <p>
    It is very much a work in progress ...
  </p>

</div>

<div class="center">
  <h2>
    <!-- Button trigger modal -->
  
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">
      Preview beta site
    </button>
    
    <!-- Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header">
            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
            <h3 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">Select a play</h3>
          </div>
          
          <div class="modal-body">
            <p><%= link_to "Preview as Beta Guest", login_path %></p>
            <p><%= link_to "Create beta user account", signup_path %></p>

          </div>
          <!--
          <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
          </div>
          -->
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </h2>
</div>
